# Transcribed from two_hop_phantom.main.cpp: seed
# e = {(1,3),(3,9),(3,4),(9,5),(1,7),(7,9)}, then one mixed batch removing
# e(3,9) and adding e(2,3). The pairing (added e(2,3), removed e(3,9)) is
# the phantom instance h(2,9), in neither the old nor the new
# materialization. Expected final h: {(1,4),(1,9),(2,4),(7,5)}.
batch
